title: 1 Bedroom Unit near Capitol Hill Area
posting_body: ['Capitol Place Apartments.', 'A modern classic located in the supremely walkable Capitol Hill.', 'This community has been tastefully updated with amenities like a private community patio, designer finishes, new appliances, hardwood floors, and large updated windows.', 'With a 96 Walkscore, daily life can be conducted easily by foot.', 'For commuters, transit is good with bus lines a block away and the light rail an under 10 min walk.', 'Bring your pets, large and small breeds are welcome!', 'Walk Score 70+, Bike Score 70+, Transit Score 70+', '1bd/1ba', '+W/D In unit', '+Vinyl Plank & Hard Wood Flooring', '+Parking Garage', 'Additional Info:', '+Utility breakdown = $90 1 person, $130 2 persons + $30 each add.', '+Property Liability Fee: $14/month', '+Electricity (Seattle City Light) & Internet – Resident responsibility', 'Move In Info:', '+Application fee: $50', '+Holding fee: $500', '+Refundable Security Deposit: 75% of 1 month’s rent', 'We are a pet friendly property!', 'No restrictions!', '+Pet rent is $50 per month+$200 refundable pet deposit']
